🎉🛍️ Download high-definition images from Dribbble shots search page with a single click to zip file, export image infos to csv file. 📸🎥

2️⃣ Export Image URLs: Gather comprehensive data about Dribbble. Export image URLs with one click. Create a CSV file for analysis, research, or any other purpose. 📊📋
